caption.p: Additional file 1 Supplementary Fig. 1. Map showing the distance between the top/ bottom 5 countries from which Dengue was imported and Kaohsiung city. The analysis chart was created after analyzing all collected imported dengue fever data from 2013 to 2018 and referring to the dengue map constructed by the Taiwan CDC ( https://cdcdengue.azurewebsites.net/Imported.aspx). The world map is publicly available via OpenStreetMap ( https://www.openstreetmap.org/).
